  "instructions": [
    "Set the ceramic tagine on medium heat and swirl in the sesame oil.",
    "Add the diced onion, minced garlic, and grated ginger, sautéing until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and vegetable broth, stirring to combine.",
    "Drop the tofu cubes into the liquid, letting them simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the soy sauce and salt, then pour the coconut cream over the mixture, creating a rich crust.",
    "Slide the halved cherry tomatoes into the tagine, covering them with the coconut layer.",
    "Cover the tagine and reduce the heat to low, simmering for 15 minutes until the tofu is tender.",
    "Uncover, sprinkle chili flakes, black pepper, and chopped cilantro, stirring gently.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, spooning the luscious coconut cream over the tofu and cherries."
